There are quite a few Preds in the CF's brig. Gangon, BrightBlade (not 
exactly in the brig), three of KSL's mercenaries, Thrash. I think that's all.

::Kluster::

Kluster nods. Dark Prime was definetly not good news.

"Ok. How can we stop him?" he asks, frowning as he suddenly notices scorch 
marks on the floors. He looks back at Valtron, waiting for the bot's responce.
